Color Palette Brand Guidelines
Color Palette

Lime Green is Glaido’s main brand color. It feels fresh, modern, and energetic,
helping the brand stand out and communicate clarity. It’s used for important
highlights, logo applications, and key interface elements.

White gives the brand space and balance. It keeps layouts clean and makes
the primary color pop. It’s the main background color for most designs.

Black provides contrast and structure. It’s used for text, and areas that need
a strong visual anchor. It helps the overall palette feel stable and
professional.

